    <h3>üõ°Ô∏è Security Features</h3>
    <table>
      <tr><th>Description / Function</th><th>Feature</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Block domains for malware, phishing, botnet, and other high-risk threats</td><td>DNS-Layer Security</td></tr>
